    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a bare-bones, budget opportunity? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 and we're being completely upfront with you! This car is showing significant wear, with mechanical issues and cosmetic damage that you'd expect from a high-mileage, well-used ride. It may need repairs to get it fully road-ready, so it's best suited for a handy buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for a parts vehicle. That said, at this price point, it's a genuine deal for the right person. Come take a look and see if it fits your needs!",
