    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 buyers should be aware of significant wear and issues throughout. The exterior shows heavy scratches, dents, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is worn with torn upholstery, damaged trim, and noticeable odors. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention, making it best suited for buyers comfortable with repairs or looking for a project vehicle or parts car. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises. Priced accordingly to reflect its true condition.",
