    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, no-frills ride that gets the job done without a hefty price tag? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it starts right up, runs, and drives, making it a genuinely practical choice for everyday commuting. You'll notice some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections that come with its age, and there may be a small repair or two on the horizon, but nothing that takes away from its core functionality. If you're a savvy buyer who appreciates honest value, this could be the right fit for you!",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and the price reflects that reality honestly. The exterior shows significant deterioration \u2014 expect deep scratches, heavy paint fading or peeling in multiple areas, rust spots, and several dents and dings across the body panels. Trim pieces may be cracked, faded, or missing entirely. The interior is worn with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged dashboard components, and general neglect throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car requires attention \u2014 it may have running issues, warning lights on the dash, or components in need of repair or replacement. It is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs parts. No warranties or guarantees are implied. Please inspect thoroughly before purchasing.",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Here's your chance to own a capable vehicle at an unbeatable entry-level price. This car is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 making it an ideal candidate for the hands-on buyer, weekend mechanic, or anyone seeking reliable basic transportation on a tight budget. What it lacks in cosmetic perfection, it makes up for in sheer affordability. Whether you're looking for a project, a parts vehicle, or simply the most economical way to get from A to B, this listing deserves a serious look. Sold as-is \u2014 priced accordingly and ready to move.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, folks! \ud83d\udc4b Got a great opportunity here for the right buyer \u2014 this one's perfect if you're a hands-on kind of person who loves a good project, or just need reliable transportation on a tight budget. She's got some wear and tear that shows she's lived a full life, but hey, that just means she's got character! A little TLC and some elbow grease could really bring her back to her former glory. Mechanically she gets you from A to B, and at this price point, you really can't go wrong. Whether you're a weekend warrior looking for a fun fixer-upper or just need something to get around town, this could be your next great adventure. Come take a look \u2014 I promise you'll be dealing with someone straight-up and friendly. Let's make a deal! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Here's a solid opportunity for the mechanically inclined buyer or weekend warrior looking for a capable platform. This unit features a proven drivetrain with the engine turning over cleanly and holding compression \u2014 the kind of foundation that responds well to attention. The transmission shifts through its gates with mechanical confidence, and the suspension geometry remains fundamentally sound. Yes, the bodywork shows the patina of real-world use, and the interior has seen better days, but the bones are there. Brakes have been recently serviced and the cooling system is functional. This is a driver-grade vehicle that gets you down the road while you build it up to your spec. Priced to reflect its current state of dress \u2014 not its potential. A strong buy for someone ready to wrench.",
      "price": 7500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    }
